Name: Aggression
Description: It’s possible to deliberately stoke the fires of Violence in Kami by traumatizing them in a very specific set of ways.

Name: Grit
Description: Refusal to die is a healthy trait.

Name: Mercenary
Description: "Why not make some money while we’re at it?”

Name: Professional
Description: A true professional understands how to play to their strengths.

Name: Cruelty
Description: Baby shark, doo-doo, doo-doo, doo-doo.

Name: Sniper
Description: Careful assessment can allow a Kami to move into a Node more quickly. A product of experience…

Name: Warmonger
Description: More fighting, more violence, more fighting, more violence.

Name: Vampire
Description: Edward Kamin, but sexier…

Name: Bandit
Description: It isn’t so much a profession as it is a way of life.

Name: Hungry
Description: You just want it more.

Name: Brutality
Description: Sheer will-to-hurt continues to go a long way.

Name: Marksman
Description: Though the craft has evolved with its medium, swift killing remains a cherished art form.

Name: Specialist
Description: Some Kami are particularly talented at preying on the weaknesses of others. They’re just like human beings in that way.

Name: First Aid
Description: Your Kami is always ready to bandage up in case of a counter-liquidation…. Meaning they can hold on to a little more musu.

Name: Bounty Hunter
Description: Your Kami is really, really good at milking all possible profit from their targets.

Name: Warlord
Description: A paragon of pure aggression. This Kamigotchi will overpower almost any other when it comes to raw strength.

Name: Lethality
Description: Liquidating a Kamigotchi requires a certain firmness of intent. This is that kind of intent.

Name: Assassin
Description: A fully-trained Assassin can enter a node almost instantly. The complacent should live in fear.

Name: Self Care
Description: Did you drink water today? Please drink water.

Name: Cardio
Description: While Kamigotchi aren’t exactly material beings, regular exercise has been proven to improve their stamina. We’re not sure why.

Name: Good Constitution
Description: Some texts from the old world refer to a similar concept, roughly translated as “breedability.”

Name: Focus
Description: It’s important to focus one’s mind on the bags.

Name: Meditative Breathing
Description: The Buteyko method emphasizes the importance of nasal breathing, which protects the airways by humidifying, warming, and cleaning the air entering the lungs.

Name: Concentration
Description: With enough concentration Kamigotchi can stave off their own death if only for a bit longer.

Name: Sleep Hygiene
Description: An element of self care. Investing in it is known to help recover one’s energy levels and physical health.

Name: Warmup Exercise
Description: Even a light warmup can offer a significant edge in physically intensive activities.

Name: Advanced Mewing
Description: Your jawline never looked so good.

Name: Momentum
Description: One does not simply achieve higher states of mind. Only after struggle and release.

Name: Therapy
Description: Or, for boys, why not blast your music while going 120mph on the highway? You don’t need this.

Name: Endurance
Description: Like many of life’s trials, Musu harvesting is often more of a marathon than a sprint.

Name: Regeneration
Description: Wolverine can do it. Starfish and salamanders can too. Stop saying “can’t” you pathetic nugget.

Name: Workout Routine
Description: 5 day split for the Serious builders.

Name: Productivity
Description: You get things done.

Name: Wu Wei
Description: Mastery of action-without-action allows you to make a little more money, with no effort. Not bad.

Name: Spin Class
Description: Cardio for the hardcore.

Name: Immortality
Description: In the same way that gliding is flying.

Name: Defensiveness
Description: Training a Kamigotchi in a certain degree of closed-mindedness can help to maintain inner peace.

Name: Toughness
Description: Without any milk.

Name: Patience
Description: Your Kamigotchi believes the virtuous should be rewarded.

Name: Meticulous
Description: When preparing for the worst, the details matter.

Name: Vigor
Description: All forms, especially libido, are a sign of good health.

Name: Armor
Description: Hard body. Battle tested. Able-to-take-a-beating kinda Kami.

Name: Anxiety
Description: aaaaAAAAaaaAaAAaAaaaaa

Name: Die Hard
Description: Survival is one thing, but another is knowing how to die effectively.

Name: Loyalty
Description: bark bark arf grrr awoof awooo

Name: Flawless
Description: They don’t want you to know your Kami can just wake up like this.

Name: Dedication
Description: Your Kami shows up 5 minutes early to literally everything.

Name: Shielding
Description: Back in my day this used to cost 30 tree branches and 50 firewood.

Name: Powerhouse
Description: All that intensive physical training has built up some Violence…

Name: Heft / Hefty
Description: Raw physical mass can be a form of talent, too.

Name: Fortress
Description: Unbreakable.

Name: Neurosis
Description: “Not a radical loss of touch with reality.”

Name: Undying
Description: Your Kami gets every single ounce of juice from their Health points.

Name: Obsession
Description: Compulsive and intrusive. But hardly a disorder.

Name: Acquisitiveness
Description: The children long for the mines…

Name: Mogging
Description: Good fashion choices can be the first step on the road to massively outsized gains.

Name: Greed
Description: Your Kami just want it more.

Name: Daylight Savings
Description: Leopold II. Hideki Tojo. George Hudson.

Name: Side Hustles
Description: Your Kamigotchi has learned to drive taxi while harvesting, increasing their MUSU gains.

Name: Hedging
Description: Go ahead. Announce your sexuality on an immutable ledger.

Name: Technical Analysis
Description: Your Kami keeps muttering about Fibonacci retracement levels. You think it may have some form of schizophrenia, but it’s making more money this way.

Name: Wide Portfolio
Description: Negatively correlated assets have proven a great way to diversify risk in your Kamigotchi’s holdings.

Name: Leverage
Description: You know how to maximise your own use of time and energy.

Name: Index Funds
Description: A way to inject some Harmony into the portfolio…

Name: Trading Courses
Description: Market capitalization? Enterprise value? he bit da wa?

Name: Opportunist
Description: Sometimes, the competition just leave themselves open.

Name: Looping
Description: You know how to get… aggressive, when harvesting MUSU.

Name: Time in the Market
Description: Always wins in the end.

Name: Stimulants
Description: For men destined to define eras and change history, who will be remembered for millennia to come.

Name: Intelligent Investor
Description: Benjamin Graham. Jim Simons. Roaring Kitty.

Name: Paid Groupchat
Description: You know it’s good. Otherwise they wouldn’t charge you.

Name: Coward
Description: What can we say? Are you actually going to choose this? We’re sure your parents still love you.
